miss_prop <- function(x){
  mean(is.na(x), na.rm = F)
}

For now, lets remove variables with > 12% missingness:

missing_indexer <- as.logical(apply(afc, 2, miss_prop)<.12)

new_afc <- afc[,missing_indexer]

ncol(afc)
## [1] 90
ncol(new_afc)
## [1] 74

And lets do a simple mean imputation on the remaining:

mode_function <- function(x) {
  ux <- unique(x)
  ux[which.max(tabulate(match(x, ux)))]
}

new_afc <- new_afc %>% 
  mutate_if(is.numeric, ~replace_na(.,mean(., na.rm = TRUE)))
